{"type": "article", "id": 27332, "title": "苹果枝桠灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-26T06:58:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021524532zvjgUkSILCfnybR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>大自然一直以来都是设计师们的灵感源泉，Ayaskan 两姐妹组成的<a href=\"http://ayaskan.com/\">双人工作室</a>最近推出了一款别致的吊灯 <a href=\"http://ayaskan.com/work/apple-branch/#\">Apple Branch</a>，让你在家抬头就能看到苹果树桠。每一个钢结构的“枝叶”连接着一个 LED 灯，晶莹剔透的玻璃灯罩模仿了果实的造型，抬头望去仿佛可以感受到苹果扑鼻的香气，十分清新。这个灯具目前还没有开始销售，想要在家里“种上一株苹果树”的还需要再等一段时间。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152450gYv7pLNDmtFJnWUO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152452hlJ4ws3QXT1ayUiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152452FHOWVoIMYGrlwyPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}